{"type":"message","id":"fb05e5e8","parentId":"ea1eba1e","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:02:47.665Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我看到更清晰的页面结构。我需要找到插件开发相关的文档。从文本中我可以看到\"插件开发 插件整体介绍 动态表单插件...\"等文本。\n\n让我尝试用JavaScript直接点击这些文本对应的链接。首先，让我找到所有包含\"插件整体介绍\"的元素并点击它。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我将使用JavaScript直接点击\"插件整体介绍\"文档："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9c98b3486ab0441f806b852a","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","kind":"evaluate","fn":"\nasync function() {\n  const allElements = document.querySelectorAll('*');\n  for (let elem of allElements) {\n    if (elem.textContent && elem.textContent.trim() === '插件整体介绍' && elem.onclick) {\n      elem.click();\n      return { success: true, message: '点击成功' };\n    }\n  }\n  return { success: false, message: '未找到' };\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":5103,"output":253,"cacheRead":62740,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68096,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774148561883}}
