{"type":"message","id":"27d2af0f","parentId":"cc8628ef","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:11:25.247Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Python环境可能不完整。让我尝试使用另一个方法：使用浏览器工具直接导出window.__NUXT__数据到文件，然后我可以在本地解析它。\n\n让我创建一个JavaScript，在浏览器中执行并保存数据到控制台，然后我可以复制它。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我尝试使用浏览器工具直接提取并保存文档数据。我将创建一个HTML文件，使用JavaScript获取数据："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5c17347bfea14a71bd3eac1a","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/extract_docs.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <title>提取金蝶文档数据</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1>提取金蝶云苍穹文档数据</h1>\n    <div id=\"output\"></div>\n    <script>\n        // 需要抓取的文档\n        const docs = [\n            '插件整体介绍',\n            '动态表单插件-插件基类',\n            '动态表单插件-视图模型',\n            '动态表单插件-数据模型',\n            '单据界面插件-插件基类',\n            '单据操作插件-插件基类',\n            '工作流插件介绍'\n        ];\n\n        // 从window.__NUXT__查找文档\n        function findDocInNuxt(nuxt, name) {\n            if (!nuxt || !nuxt.data || !nuxt.data[0]) return null;\n\n            const catList = nuxt.data[0].categoryList || [];\n\n            function search(items, targetName) {\n                for (let item of items) {\n                    if (item.name === targetName && item.entityType === 'Knowledge') {\n                        return item;\n                    }\n                    if (item.childCategory) {\n                        const found = search(item.childCategory, targetName);\n                        if (found) return found;\n                    }\n                }\n                return null;\n            }\n\n            return search(catList, name);\n        }\n\n        // 显示结果\n        function showResults() {\n            const output = document.getElementById('output');\n            const nuxt = window.__NUXT__;\n\n            if (!nuxt) {\n                output.innerHTML = '<p style=\"color: red;\">window.__NUXT__ 未找到</p>';\n                return;\n            }\n\n            const results = docs.map(docName => {\n                const docInfo = findDocInNuxt(nuxt, docName);\n                return {\n                    name: docName,\n                    found: !!docInfo,\n                    id: docInfo ? docInfo.id : null,\n                    entityId: docInfo ? docInfo.entityId : null,\n                    parentId: docInfo ? docInfo.parentId : null\n                };\n            });\n\n            output.innerHTML = '<pre>' + JSON.stringify(results, null, 2) + '</pre>';\n\n            // 同时保存到localStorage\n            localStorage.setItem('kingdee_docs', JSON.stringify(results));\n            console.log('结果已保存到 localStorage.kingdee_docs');\n        }\n\n        // 在页面加载完成后显示\n        window.onload = function() {\n            setTimeout(showResults, 1000);\n        };\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":16,"output":691,"cacheRead":66206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66913,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774149074739}}
