{"type":"message","id":"94d05b42","parentId":"2d849913","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:12:25.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！我找到了window.__NUXT__的完整数据。从这大量的JSON数据中，我可以看到需要抓取的文档ID。让我用Python解析这个HTML文件，提取需要的文档ID。\n\n从数据中我可以看到：\n- \"插件整体介绍\" 的 entityId: \"239045906702872064\", id: \"246687662705454080\"\n- \"动态表单插件-插件基类\" 的 entityId: \"221658844169026560\", id: \"238600436469803520\"\n- \"动态表单插件-视图模型\" 的 entityId: \"221674425806898944\", id: \"238600471047645696\"\n- \"动态表单插件-数据模型\" 的 entityId: \"221682121566163200\", id: \"238600498478189568\"\n- \"单据界面插件-插件基类\" 的 entityId: \"223122193297751040\", id: \"238604724860430848\"\n- \"单据操作插件-插件基类\" 的 entityId: \"225548911090181376\", id: \"238612133964295168\"\n- \"工作流插件介绍\" 的 entityId: \"24194\", id: \"263693539911803136\"\n\n现在我需要使用浏览器工具逐个访问这些文档页面并抓取内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"完美！我找到了window.__NUXT__数据。现在让我解析文档ID并开始抓取："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7d789b825bca483495968a18","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\n# 需要抓取的文档\ndocs = [\n    '插件整体介绍',\n    '动态表单插件-插件基类',\n    '动态表单插件-视图模型',\n    '动态表单插件-数据模型',\n    '单据界面插件-插件基类',\n    '单据操作插件-插件基类',\n    '工作流插件介绍'\n]\n\n# 读取HTML文件\nwith open('/tmp/kingdee_page.html', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# 查找window.__NUXT__\nimport re\nmatch = re.search(r'window\\.__NUXT__\\s*=\\s*\\((function[^<]+)\\);', content, re.DOTALL)\n\nif match:\n    # 提取JSON数据\n    js_code = match.group(1)\n    \n    # 提取文档ID的正则\n    for doc in docs:\n        pattern = f'\"{doc}\"[^}}]*\"entityId\":\"([^\"]+)\"[^}}]*\"id\":\"([^\"]+)\"'\n        m = re.search(pattern, content)\n        if m:\n            print(f\"{doc} | ID: {m.group(2)} | EntityID: {m.group(1)}\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"{doc} | 未找到\")\n\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":89803,"output":994,"cacheRead":9821,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100618,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774149122001}}
