{"type":"message","id":"f25dc955","parentId":"6345fded","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:12:38.095Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"正则表达式匹配有问题。让我换一个方法，直接提取window.__NUXT__，然后使用exec()的JavaScript能力来处理。或者，我可以直接使用浏览器工具，通过JavaScript提取数据。\n\n让我直接在浏览器中执行JavaScript来提取文档ID，然后逐个访问抓取。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我直接在浏览器中提取文档ID并开始抓取："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7db8978818fa4bfa8183ddcb","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act<arg_key>kind</arg_key><arg_value>evaluate","fn":"\n() => {\n  const docs = [\n    '插件整体介绍',\n    '动态表单插件-插件基类',\n    '动态表单插件-视图模型',\n    '动态表单插件-数据模型',\n    '单据界面插件-插件基类',\n    '单据操作插件-插件基类',\n    '工作流插件介绍'\n  ];\n  \n  const nuxt = window.__NUXT__;\n  if (!nuxt || !nuxt.data || !nuxt.data[0]) {\n    return { error: 'No nuxt data' };\n  }\n  \n  const catList = nuxt.data[0].categoryList || [];\n  \n  function search(items, name) {\n    for (let item of items) {\n      if (item.name === name && item.entityType === 'Knowledge') {\n        return { id: item.id, entityId: item.entityId };\n      }\n      if (item.childCategory) {\n        const found = search(item.childCategory, name);\n        if (found) return found;\n      }\n    }\n    return null;\n  }\n  \n  const results = {};\n  docs.forEach(doc => {\n    const info = search(catList, doc);\n    if (info) {\n      results[doc] = info;\n    }\n  });\n  \n  return results;\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":11,"output":426,"cacheRead":100847,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101284,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774149152993}}
