{"type":"message","id":"c3b99a0a","parentId":"3fd8b8be","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:18:05.424Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_980595a851ba4061b3f84469","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"To answer your questions:  \n\n### 1. Is the \"插件开发\" (Plugin Development) section visible in the left sidebar?  \nYes, the \"插件开发\" (Plugin Development) section is visible in the left sidebar.  \n\n\n### 2. What documents are listed under \"插件开发\"?  \nUnder the \"插件开发\" section, documents related to plugin development are listed. From the context, one of the key documents is **\"动态表单插件-插件基类\" (Dynamic Form Plugin - Plugin Base Class)**, which is a core reference for developing dynamic form plugins. Other potential documents (depending on the full list) might include related plugin development guides, but \"动态表单插件-插件基类\" is a prominent entry.  \n\n\n### 3. Can you identify \"动态表单插件-插件基类\" in the list?  \nYes, \"动态表单插件-插件基类\" is identifiable in the list under the \"插件开发\" section. It appears as a specific document focused on the foundational class for dynamic form plugins, serving as a key resource for developers working on plugin implementation.  \n\n\n### Overall Observation  \nThe left sidebar organizes content into sections (e.g., \"快速开始\", \"基础\", \"前端组件和页面开发\", \"模型管理\", \"权限中心\", \"流程引擎\", \"插件开发\"). The \"插件开发\" section contains technical documentation for building plugins, with \"动态表单插件-插件基类\" being a notable entry for developers targeting dynamic form functionality."}],"details":{"model":"zai/glm-4.6v","image":"/root/.openclaw/media/browser/ed5e6820-a007-45c9-b26e-0802c2685821.png","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774149485415}}
